FBIS4-7649 "dreeu064__a94004" FBIS-EEU-94-064-A Daily Report 2 Apr 1994 ANNEX Albania Greek Police Expel 800 Nationals to Kakavije Greek Police Expel 800 Nationals to Kakavije AU0204135494 Tirana ATA in English 1008 GMT 2 Apr 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU0204135494 Tirana ATA English BFN [Text] Gjirokaster, April 2 (ATA) -- Some 800 Albanians have been expelled from Greece over the Kakavije border crossing point during the past three days. The average number of expelles reached 230 a day. Some of the Albanians have been working in Greece for years with regular visas. They were abused, their money was confiscated, and their passports were torn to pieces.
